var x, y, z; var u = f(x, y, z); double [ux, uy, uz] = derivatives(u, wrt(x, y, z));
dual x, y, z; dual u = f(x, y, z); double ux = derivative(f, wrt(x), at(x, y, z)); double uy = derivative(f, wrt(y), at(x, y, z)); double uz = derivative(f, wrt(z), at(x, y, z));
